title: Hide And Creep  (MKV)
description:
R | 1h 25min | Comedy, Horror | September 23rd 2004




Residents of a small Southern town contend with bloodthirsty zombies, a mysterious flying saucer, and bad television reception.




Directors: Chuck Hartsell, Chance Shirley

Writer: Chance Shirley

Stars: Chuck Hartsell, Michael Shelton, Kyle Holman




Extras include the short film Birthday Call,Behind A Scene-Bob's Live Bait and feature commentary.


Widescreen Presentation,English Audio
